      "role": "user",
      "content": "Sometimes I look in the mirror and I dont even see a person anymore. It feels like the version of me that actually lived, the one with dreams and a future, died a long time ago. I'm just... a ghost inhabiting a body that keeps moving because it has to. I'm just a walking corpse at this point.",
